  m_text: 'When the game starts, enemies will spawn in waves. You, the player, will
    have a base at the end of the enemies their route that you will have to protect
    to survive the game.


    You protect your base by placing towers on the empty
    tiles surrounding the enemy their path.


    Every enemy defeated gains you
    money to buy offensive and support towers. Towers can also be upgraded with your
    coins, increasing attack power, speed or range.'
